quran[9]{c,v,t,f}:
  12,94,"Sano ndema jawaŵigwile nkutula (kuujila kumangwao), baba ŵao (ŵali Yaakubu ŵaŵaliji pa jele ndemajo ku Shami) ŵatite: “Chisimu une ngupikana luumba lwa Yusufu, ingaŵaga kuti nkuunganichisya yakusokonechela lunda (nkangulupilile).”"
  12,95,"Ŵanganyao ŵatite: “Tukunnumbila Allah! Chisimutu mmwe n’di mu kusoya kwenu kwakala (kwakunnonyela nnope Yusufu).”"
  12,96,"Basi ndema jajwaiche nkujigala abali jakusengwasya, jwajiponyisye (kansu ja Yusufu) pangope jakwe (ja Yaakubu), basi papopo ŵatandite soni kulola. Ŵatite: “Ana nganimbecheta kukwenu yanti une ngumanyilila kuumila kwa Allah yangankuimanyilila jenumanja?”"
  14,40,"“Ambuje ŵangu! Mundendani une kuŵa jwakwimika Swala mwakolosya, nambo soni ni achiŵanangu ŵakwe. Ambuje ŵetu! Pochelani soni duwa jangu.”"
  14,41,"“Ambuje ŵetu! Timungululuchile une ni achinangolo ŵangu ŵaŵili, kwisa soni ŵakulupilila, lisiku lya chichisimichika chiŵalanjilo.”"
  14,42,"Soni ngasin’ganichisya ata panandi yanti Allah ngajukuimanya yaakutenda ŵalupuso, nambo kuti jugamba kwachelewasya kwikanila lisiku lyachigakolondoka mu lyele (lisikulyo) meso."
  15,13,"Ngakasajikulupililaga jalakwe (Qur’an) kutendaga pamasile payapite ilandanyo ya (ŵandu) ŵandanda (yaŵatite kapedwe ipotesi)."
  15,14,"Soni tungaaugulile (achimakafilio) nnango wakwinani, ni kuŵa ŵanganyao ali nkukwela kwalakweko chitetete (mwaakusachila, kuti chiŵe chisimosimo cha Muhammadi ﷺ)."
  15,15,"Basi angatite: “Chisimu meso getu gantesile ndandagasi. (Ngwamba), nambo kuti uwwe ni ŵandu ŵakulogwa (tukuiona ikaliyo).”"